This plugin's sound-pack format and its conventions for naming Steam UI
sound events are interoperable with the SDH-AudioLoader Decky-Loader
plugin:

  https://github.com/DeckThemes/SDH-AudioLoader
  Copyright (c) 2022 EMERALD0874 (MIT) / Steam Deck Homebrew (BSD-3-Clause)

No source code from SDH-AudioLoader was copied or transliterated. The
Decky-AudioLoader filename → event mapping in `backend.ts` exists so
that existing community sound packs work without conversion; the
filenames themselves are facts about the Steam UI's sound assets, not
creative expression of the SDH-AudioLoader project.

The community pack registry consumed by this plugin is hosted at
api.deckthemes.com and operated by the DeckThemes community. Pack
metadata and zip downloads are fetched live from that API at runtime;
no registry snapshot is bundled with this plugin. Each installed pack
records its upstream attribution in `pack-meta.json` alongside the
audio files.
